scenario message msg ShouldPrintWhenPlayerMoves direction FromCavern cavern
put player in cavern @cavern
enter command rest
reject message @msg was printed
enter command @direction
ensure message @msg was printed

scenario message msg should print when player approaches object
put @object in cavern 3
message @msg should print when player moves west from cavern 5
message @msg should print when player moves east from cavern 1
message @msg should print when player moves north from cavern 9
message @msg should print when player moves south from cavern 6
If the wumpus is in any adjacent cavern, you should be able to smell it.

To do this we'll freeze the wumpus so that it doesn't move around.
Then we'll place the player near the Wumpus and see if the "Smell" message is emitted.

 Included page: <HuntTheWumpus.CrossMap (edit)
Create a convenient map that looks like this:

         [6]
         [7]
   [1][2][3][4][5]
         [8]
         [9]


Make map
start end direction
1 2 E
2 3 E
3 4 E
4 5 E
6 7 S
7 3 S
3 8 S
8 9 S

script
freeze wumpus true

script
message You smell the Wumpus. should print when player approaches wumpus
Scenario
scenario message msg should print when player approaches object
put wumpus in cavern 3
message You smell the Wumpus. should print when player moves west from cavern 5
Scenario
scenario message msg ShouldPrintWhenPlayerMoves direction FromCavern cavern
put player in cavern 5
enter command rest
reject message You smell the Wumpus. was printed
enter command west
ensure message You smell the Wumpus. was printed
message You smell the Wumpus. should print when player moves east from cavern 1
Scenario
scenario message msg ShouldPrintWhenPlayerMoves direction FromCavern cavern
put player in cavern 1
enter command rest
reject message You smell the Wumpus. was printed
enter command east
ensure message You smell the Wumpus. was printed
message You smell the Wumpus. should print when player moves north from cavern 9
Scenario
scenario message msg ShouldPrintWhenPlayerMoves direction FromCavern cavern
put player in cavern 9
enter command rest
reject message You smell the Wumpus. was printed
enter command north
ensure message You smell the Wumpus. was printed
message You smell the Wumpus. should print when player moves south from cavern 6
Scenario
scenario message msg ShouldPrintWhenPlayerMoves direction FromCavern cavern
put player in cavern 6
enter command rest
reject message You smell the Wumpus. was printed
enter command south
ensure message You smell the Wumpus. was printed
